Rabat is a road movie that takes the viewer on a journey of three friends Nadir (Nasrdin Dchar), Abdel (Achmed Akkabi) and Zakaria (Chico Kenzari). As Nadir from one day to the old taxi from his father to drive from London to Rabat, his two best friends invite themselves to join him to go. The journey takes the trio through the European countryside to the Moroccan capital. New worlds, encounters on the road and the secret destination of Nadir put the friendship closer they come under increasing pressure Rabat.
